programme.title: Did I Mention Invention?

programme.title: Di-Gata Defenders
programme.desc: On the run from Malco and Flinch and The Sand Nomads who have overrun the Dojo, Mel and Erik encounter Bo, a brash young stone slinger who tells them of a warrior cult competition being held in a nearby county.

programme.title: Di-Gata Defenders
programme.desc: With the help of Rion, Mel escapes Lady Ktahsh but the Ethos have captured SiI, a monstrously powerful guardian! Back at the Dojo Seth becomes suspicious of Kara and traps her, only to discover she is the shape shifter Kali!

programme.title: Di-Gata Defenders
programme.desc: Erik is kidnapped by a carnival of misfits and the Defenders must fight to get him back.

programme.title: Di-Gata Defenders
programme.desc: When a mining village is terrorized by Kid Cole, Erik and Rion respond to the call for help while Seth and Mel go in search of Malco and Flinch.

programme.title: Di-Gata Defenders
programme.desc: With the Dojo under siege by the army of Sigil Slayers, the Mortagarians arrive and join forces with the Defenders to beat back Lady KTahsh and the Sigil slayers.

programme.title: Di-Gata Defenders
programme.desc: On their way to the Monastery of Amos-Yan to recover The Key, a device which will lead them to the four pure stones, Seth and his fellow Di-Gata Defenders are ambushed by a band of thieves.

programme.title: Di-Gata Defenders
programme.desc: Kara is still feeling the effects of the spider poison, and Mel is suffering from spontaneous and draining eruptions of psychic power, The Defenders head for the legendary Nexus, over the centuries a traditional place of healing for Di-Gata defenders.

programme.title: Di-Gata Defenders
programme.desc: Seth learns the hard way that looks can be deceiving when the attentions of a pretty girl lead the Defenders to face destruction in a village where, literally, nothing is as it seems.

programme.title: Di-Gata Defenders
programme.desc: Erik, Rion and Brackus head to the island of Rivas to meet up with Seth and Mel and help find Brim the stonecutter.

programme.title: Di-Gata Defenders
programme.desc: Kara is double-crossed by Brackus and must find a way home from the Dark Realm by herself.

programme.title: Di-Gata Defenders
programme.desc: The Defenders find that a walled city held in the grasp of a ruthless dictator has a dark secret.

programme.title: Di-Gata Defenders
programme.desc: Mel learns that one of the pieces of the Celestial Abyss is at the Temple of Yan-Mara.

programme.title: Di-Gata Defenders
programme.desc: The Defenders find the way to the pure stone is blocked by the Dakonauts, Lord Nazmul's unstoppable robotic army.

programme.title: Di-Gata Defenders
programme.desc: When Seths arm is gravely injured during a surprise attack by KTahsh, the Defenders travel to Mau-data to heal him where they find Adam.

programme.title: Di-Gata Defenders
programme.desc: For the first time in their lives, the defenders find themselves on the high seas and discover that their Di-Gata stones dont work over water!

programme.title: Di-Gata Defenders
programme.desc: Deep in the bowels of an abandoned mine, the Defenders uncover a secret destined to shake the entire realm of Rados to its foundations: The existence of a Ninth Sigil.

programme.title: Di-Gata Defenders
programme.desc: At the place of binding, the defenders find themselves under attack. Brackus has raised an army against them.

programme.title: Di-Gata Defenders
programme.desc: Adam and Erik rescue a seemingly innocent Maiden, only to discover that she isnt quite the victim she made herself out to be.

programme.title: Di-Gata Defenders
programme.desc: After the Defenders discover that Doku and a group of warlords are planning to take control of Rados, Seth gets wounded as a result of Rion jumping in to an attack.

programme.title: Di-Gata Defenders
programme.desc: Eluding bounty hunters, the rascally Adam charms his way into the Defenders encampment only to steal away in the night with their pure stones.

programme.title: Di-Gata Defenders
programme.desc: Mel dreams of a long lost monastery and a pure stone hidden there.

programme.title: Di-Gata Defenders
programme.desc: Flinch coerces the Zads into an alliance with the Ethos. Brackus tells the Defenders that Malco intends to use the orb of Ogama-Yan to find five parts of a super weapon called The Celestial Abyss.

programme.title: Di-Gata Defenders
programme.desc: The Defenders encounter a cocky young Stone Slinger eager to make a name for himself by challenging Seth to a showdown. An unlikely ally (Adam) is discovered inside the Stone Slingers gang.

programme.title: Di-Gata Defenders
programme.desc: After almost causing the destruction of Arboth, Seth decides to leave the other Defenders.

programme.title: Di-Gata Defenders

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S1E1) Chilean drug chemist Cockroach brings his product to Colombian smuggler Pablo Escobar. DEA agent Steve Murphy joins the war on drugs in Bogota.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S1E2) Communist radical group M-19 makes a move against the narcos, while Murphy gets an education in Colombian law enforcement from his new partner Peña.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S1E3) Murphy encounters the depths of government corruption when he and Peña try to derail Escobar's political ambitions by proving he's narco.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S1E4) Despite a new extradition treaty, the U.S. puts more money into fighting communism, creating new challenges for Murphy and Peña in the hunt for Pablo.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S1E5) Pablo's extreme methods put the narcos on the brink of war with Carillo and the government. Peña tries to protect his witness.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S1E6) Peña and Carillo close in on Gacha. Murphy tries to protect pro-extradition candidate Gaviria from a notorious assassin connected to Pablo.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S1E7) Pablo goes into hiding as the political tide turns against him, but he finds a way to strike back. Murphy and Peña finally get the CIA to help them.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S1E8) A tragic mistake forces the government to change tactics in the fight against Pablo. But Pablo faces bigger threats from inside his empire.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S1E9) The hunt for Pablo seems to be over after he makes a deal with the government, but Murphy and Peña - and the Cali Cartel - have other plans.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S1E10) Pablo's activities in prison provoke the government into taking extreme action. Murphy and Peña face a situation of their own.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S2E1) In the aftermath of a massive military effort to take Pablo into custody, the family reunites while enemies worry. Steve and Connie fight about safety.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S2E2) Tata gets impatient with life on the run. Pablo responds to President Gaviria’s reward offer. Steve and Javier meet their new boss.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S2E3) President Gaviria has a new job for an old colleague. The Search Bloc's new tactic shake up Pablo, but also unsettle Steve and Javier.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S2E4) The Cali Cartel discusses moving in on Pablo's territory. Límon proposes a plan to Maritza. Tata gets a gun for protection.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S2E5) The Search Bloc gets a new leader. Javier loses faith in the system. Pablo brings Tata's brother Carlos down from Miami to cheer her up.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S2E6) The newly-formed Los Pepes want to destroy Pablo and his empire. Tata's brother urges her to leave and seek safety with her children.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S2E7) As the danger intensifies for the Escobars, Pablo sends his family to another country. Gaviria weighs the opportunity to use them as leverage.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S2E4) El Cartel de Cali hace planes para adueñarse del territorio de Pablo. Limón propone un plan a Maritza. Tata obtiene una pistola para su protección.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S2E5) Hay un nuevo líder en el bloque de búsqueda. Javier ya no cree en el sistema. Pablo trae a Carlos de Miami para animar a Tata.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S2E6) El recién formado Cartel de Los Pepes decide destruir a Pablo y a su Imperio. Carlos conseja a Tata que escape a un lugar seguro con sus hijos.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S2E7) Ante el inminente peligro para los Escobar, Pablo envía su familia a otro país. Gaviria ve la oportunidad para usarlos como moneda de cambio.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S2E8) Colombia le da la espalda a Escobar después de un ataque terrorista. Tata recibe ayuda de un aliado inesperado. Quica sufre de ansiedad.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S2E9) Pablo se reune con un familiar lejano. La vida de July Moncada está en peligro. La DEA y la CIA no se ponen de acuerdo en una estrategia para enfrentar a Los Pepes.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S2E10) Javier sufre las consecuencias por la entrevista de Judy. Tata intenta convencer a Pablo para que se rinda por el bien de los niños.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S3E1) En una reunión del Cartel de Cali, los jefes hacen un anuncio inesperado sobre el futuro del negocio.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S3E2) Jorge interviene para rescatar el acuerdo de cooperación entre el cartel de Cali y el gobierno después de un incidente. Peña tiene problemas con su contacto en los Pepes.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S3E3) Los hermanos Rodríguez se esconden durante las negociaciones. Pacho conoce al Señor de los Cielos en México. El nuevo equipo de Peña en la DEA visita Cali.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S3E4) Peña tiene un nuevo plan para capturar a Gilberto Rodríguez, líder del cartel de Cali. Amado propone un negocio a Pacho.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S3E5) Paranoico ante posibles filtraciones, Miguel aumenta su seguridad. Pacho le da una respuesta a Amado. Peña busca testigos.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S3E6) Jorge toma un gran riesgo. Un accidente en Nueva York podría exponer a Chepe. Peña viaja a Curaçao para arrestar a un testigo potencial.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S3E7) Peña planea un nuevo operativo para capturar a un integrante del cartel de Cali.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S3E8) David quiere vengar a su padre y en el intento pone a Enrique en peligro. Peña pide ayuda a Don Berna en una misión de rescate.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S3E9) David sigue una corazonada. Peña se sorprende ante el nivel de corrupción en el gobierno colombiano.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S3E10) David y Peña están en una carrera para encontrar a Palomari. Peña toma una decisión importante sobre su futuro.

programme.title: Narcos: México (LAS)
programme.desc: (S1E1) Cuando el ejercito arrasa los plantíos de Marihuana en Sinaloa, un ambicioso agricultor planea trasladar las operaciones de su naciente imperio a Guadalajara. Un joven agente de la DEA es transferido a México.
